{
  "version": "1.0",
  "lastUpdated": "2026-05-19",
  "description": "百草行 - 序章剧情数据（S01-S09）",
  "storyId": "prologue",
  "title": "序章·结业·灵宠·启程",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "S01",
      "name": "开场黑屏独白",
      "type": "monologue",
      "duration": 45,
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "S01_001",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "大草纪，中历三百四十七年秋。",
          "textColorStart": "#8a7050",
          "textColorEnd": "#8a7050",
          "bgColor": "#000000",
          "sound": null,
          "nextDelay": 2000
        },
        {
          "id": "S01_002",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "华夏大地本草繁盛，山野之间，随处可见药农弯腰采摘的身影。",
          "textColorStart": "#9a8060",
          "textColorEnd": "#9a8060",
          "bgColor": "#000000",
          "sound": null,
          "nextDelay": 2000
        },
        {
          "id": "S01_003",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "然自两年前起，各地陆续有传言——山中出现一种从未见过的灰绿色草，所经之处，寸草不生。",
          "textColorStart": "#b89070",
          "textColorEnd": "#b89070",
          "bgColor": "#000000",
          "sound": null,
          "nextDelay": 2000
        },
        {
          "id": "S01_004",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "百姓称之为「蛊根草」。",
          "textColorStart": "#d4a880",
          "textColorEnd": "#d4a880",
          "bgColor": "#000000",
          "sound": null,
          "nextDelay": 2000
        },
        {
          "id": "S01_005",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "而此时，岐黄学堂，一个年轻的医者，即将结业。",
          "textColorStart": "#e8c8a0",
          "textColorEnd": "#f0e8d4",
          "bgColor": "#000000",
          "sound": null,
          "nextDelay": 500,
          "triggerFadeIn": true,
          "nextScene": "S02"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S02",
      "name": "岐黄学堂·清晨",
      "type": "scene",
      "duration": 90,
      "background": "bg_school_yard.png",
      "bgm": "bgm_school.mp3",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "S02_001",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "岐黄学堂，今日清晨格外静谧。",
          "nextDelay": 2000
        },
        {
          "id": "S02_002",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "三年时光匆匆，今日，是你在这里的最后一天。",
          "nextDelay": 2000,
          "nextScene": "S03"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S03",
      "name": "结业典礼·白院长对话",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "duration": 180,
      "background": "bg_school_yard.png",
      "bgm": "bgm_school.mp3",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "S03_001",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "孩子，在这学堂，你已勤修三载。今日结业，老夫甚是欣慰。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S03_002",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "本草之道，非书中所能尽述。真正的医者，须以山川为师，以百姓为鉴。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S03_003",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "thoughtful",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "只是……你此番出行，心中可有把握？",
          "avatar": "bai_thoughtful.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S03_choice1",
          "type": "choice",
          "options": [
            {
              "text": "院长所传，学生铭记于心，自当竭力。",
              "flag": "confident",
              "response": {
                "character": "bai",
                "expression": "smile",
                "name": "白院长",
                "text": "（欣慰地点头）好，有此心气，前路虽远，终能到达。",
                "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
                "nextDelay": 500,
                "nextStep": "S03_004"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "学生尚浅，还望院长多加指点……",
              "flag": "humble",
              "response": {
                "character": "bai",
                "expression": "smile",
                "name": "白院长",
                "text": "（温和地笑）无妨，行医之路本就是边行边学。为师也曾如此走来。",
                "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
                "nextDelay": 500,
                "nextStep": "S03_004"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "只是想亲眼看看山川，看看百姓。",
              "flag": "curious",
              "response": {
                "character": "bai",
                "expression": "thoughtful",
                "name": "白院长",
                "text": "（眼中闪过赞许）好孩子，医者之心，正在此处。",
                "avatar": "bai_thoughtful.png",
                "nextDelay": 500,
                "nextStep": "S03_004"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "S03_004",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "（点头）很好。结业之前，老夫还有最后一课要教你——随我去药圃吧。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S03_005",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "thoughtful",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "那里种着学堂最珍贵的几味药草。你且仔细看，日后行走江湖，这些可是救命的宝贝。",
          "avatar": "bai_thoughtful.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S03_006",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "（跟随白院长穿过回廊，空气中渐渐弥漫起草木的清香……）",
          "nextDelay": 1500,
          "nextScene": "S04"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S04",
      "name": "药圃·识药与采药",
      "type": "scene",
      "duration": 300,
      "background": "herb_garden_bg",
      "bgm": "bgm_school.mp3",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "S04_001",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "药圃之中，阳光透过竹帘洒落，各色草药在微风中轻轻摇曳。",
          "nextDelay": 1500
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_002",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "（走到一株植物前，蹲下身来）来，你且看——这株是甘草。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "overlayImage": "gancao_closeup",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_003",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "你看它的叶片，卵圆形，边缘有细齿；茎直立，表面有柔毛。记住这个样子。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "overlayImage": "gancao_closeup",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_choice1",
          "type": "choice",
          "options": [
            {
              "text": "（仔细观察）叶片卵圆，边缘有细齿……我记住了！",
              "flag": "careful_observation",
              "response": {
                "character": "bai",
                "expression": "smile",
                "name": "白院长",
                "text": "（赞许地点头）很好，观察入微是医者的基本功。现在走近它，亲手采一株试试。",
                "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
                "nextDelay": 500,
                "nextStep": "S04_tutorial_1"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "院长，甘草有什么功效呢？",
              "flag": "ask_effect",
              "response": {
                "character": "bai",
                "expression": "thoughtful",
                "name": "白院长",
                "text": "问得好。甘草味甘性平，能补脾益气、润肺止咳，更有调和诸药之能。被誉为「国老」，你且去采一株来。",
                "avatar": "bai_thoughtful.png",
                "nextDelay": 500,
                "nextStep": "S04_tutorial_1"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_tutorial_1",
          "type": "tutorial",
          "tutorialAction": "highlight_herb",
          "herbId": "gancao",
          "hint": "靠近甘草（金色光圈标记），走进半径50px以内触发交互（点击屏幕可跳过）",
          "hintPosition": "bottom",
          "pulseColor": 16766720,
          "skippable": true,
          "nextDelay": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_tutorial_2",
          "type": "tutorial",
          "tutorialAction": "show_collect_prompt",
          "hint": "出现采集提示 ——·E 采集 甘草·—— ，按 E 键开始采集（点击屏幕可跳过）",
          "hintPosition": "bottom",
          "skippable": true,
          "nextDelay": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_tutorial_3",
          "type": "tutorial",
          "tutorialAction": "play_collect_animation",
          "hint": "播放采集动画（主角蹲下，绿色粒子飘散）→ 屏幕右上 +甘草×1 浮字（点击屏幕可跳过）",
          "hintPosition": "bottom",
          "skippable": true,
          "nextDelay": 1000
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_tutorial_4",
          "type": "tutorial",
          "tutorialAction": "open_backpack",
          "hint": "引导：「按 B 键或点击背包图标」查看刚采集的甘草",
          "hintPosition": "bottom",
          "nextDelay": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_005",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "（看着你手中的甘草，微微点头）不错。甘草，味甘性平，归心肺脾胃经。能补脾益气，润肺止咳，调和诸药。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "unlockHerb": "gancao",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_006",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "再来认识一味常用药——菊花。（走向右侧花丛）这便是了。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "overlayImage": "juhua_closeup",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_007",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "thoughtful",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "菊花，疏散风热、平肝明目。秋日采摘最佳，此时药力最盛。你去采两株回来。",
          "avatar": "bai_thoughtful.png",
          "overlayImage": "juhua_closeup",
          "unlockHerb": "juhua",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_tutorial_5",
          "type": "tutorial",
          "tutorialAction": "collect_juhua",
          "herbId": "juhua",
          "requiredCount": 2,
          "hint": "去采集菊花×2（靠近后按E），进度：0/2",
          "hintPosition": "bottom",
          "nextDelay": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_008",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "serious",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "（满意地看着你的收获）记住——不同节气，草药药性有别；晨露未干时采摘，效力最佳。这是老夫毕生的经验。",
          "avatar": "bai_serious.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_009",
          "type": "reward",
          "items": [
            { "id": "gancao", "name": "甘草", "count": 1, "icon": "🌿" },
            { "id": "juhua", "name": "菊花", "count": 2, "icon": "🌼" }
          ],
          "nextDelay": 1200
        },
        {
          "id": "S04_010",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "这些草药先收好，日后必有用处。随我来，灵药房还有一样东西要交给你。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "nextDelay": 500,
          "nextScene": "S05"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S05",
      "name": "灵药房·灵宠觉醒",
      "type": "scene",
      "duration": 200,
      "background": "yaofang_bg",
      "bgm": "bgm_spirit.mp3",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "S05_001",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "跟随白院长走进灵药房，室内光线柔和，空气中弥漫着一股奇异的草木气息。",
          "nextDelay": 1500
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_002",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "（走到石台前，指向三枚散发着微光的卵石）这些，是学堂代代相传的灵宠之卵。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "overlayImage": "eshi_closeup",
          "hidePortrait": true,
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_003",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "thoughtful",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "它们沉睡已久，只在有缘人靠近时才会苏醒。今日你结业，或有一枚与你有缘……上前感受一番吧。",
          "avatar": "bai_thoughtful.png",
          "overlayImage": "eshi_closeup",
          "hidePortrait": true,
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_004",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "（你缓缓走向那三枚卵石。当你的手即将触碰到中间那枚淡绿色卵石的瞬间——）",
          "nextDelay": 1500
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_pet_select",
          "type": "pet_selection",
          "pets": [
            {
              "id": "qingmiao",
              "name": "青苗",
              "type": "plant",
              "color": "#4a8c5c",
              "description": "天赋：感知草木灵气，率先感知草药位置。擅长：寻药、辨药品质。",
              "available": true
            },
            {
              "id": "dancheng",
              "name": "丹橙",
              "type": "fire",
