              "type": "water",
              "color": "#4a7ca8",
              "description": "天赋：溪涧感知，水边草药产量加成。擅长：溪谷采集、水煎。",
              "available": false,
              "unavailableText": "暂无缘分"
            }
          ],
          "nextDelay": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_awakening",
          "type": "cg",
          "cgId": "CG_03",
          "cgConfig": {
            "image": "cg_03_awakening.png",
            "fadeInDuration": 800,
            "animation": "awakening",
            "petId": "qingmiao"
          },
          "nextDelay": 1000
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_005",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "（卵石表面泛起翠绿色的光芒，一道温润的光芒从其中透出——一个小小的身影渐渐浮现。）",
          "nextDelay": 2000
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_006",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "qingmiao",
          "expression": "surprised",
          "name": "青苗",
          "text": "（揉着眼睛，迷迷糊糊地坐起）唔……好亮的光……是哪里……？",
          "avatar": "qingmiao_surprised.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_007",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "qingmiao",
          "expression": "happy",
          "name": "青苗",
          "text": "（猛地睁大眼睛，惊喜地跳起来）呀——！！是主人！主人的气息！青苗……青苗认识主人！！",
          "avatar": "qingmiao_happy.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_008",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "qingmiao",
          "expression": "surprised",
          "name": "青苗",
          "text": "（绕着你飞了一圈，停在你肩头）青苗等了好久好久！终于等到主人了！以后青苗帮主人找好多好多草药！",
          "avatar": "qingmiao_surprised.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_009",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "（眼中满是欣慰）看来它认准你了。青苗是草木之灵，能感知方圆百里内的药草气息。此行有它在侧，如虎添翼。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "setPet": "qingmiao",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S05_010",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "qingmiao",
          "expression": "happy",
          "name": "青苗",
          "text": "（骄傲地挺胸）哼哼！青苗很厉害的！主人去哪青苗就去哪！永远在一起！",
          "avatar": "qingmiao_happy.png",
          "nextDelay": 500,
          "nextScene": "S06"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "S06",
      "name": "学堂门口·送别与行囊准备",
      "type": "scene",
      "duration": 160,
      "background": "bg_school_gate.png",
      "bgm": "bgm_school.mp3",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "S06_001",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "正准备整理行囊，学堂的杂役小兰气喘吁吁地跑来——",
          "nextDelay": 1500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_002",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "xiaolan",
          "expression": "anxious",
          "name": "小兰",
          "text": "（上气不接下气）师兄/师姐！等一下！院长让我给你送东西来了！",
          "avatar": "xiaolan_anxious.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_003",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "xiaolan",
          "expression": "grateful",
          "name": "小兰",
          "text": "（从身后拿出一个布袋）这是院长为你准备的行医背囊，里面还有两百文铜钱和一封推荐信。",
          "avatar": "xiaolan_grateful.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_004",
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "（你接过沉甸甸的背囊，打开一看——整齐的内衬、分格的草药槽，还有夹层里的铜钱和推荐信。）",
          "nextDelay": 1800
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_005",
          "type": "reward",
          "items": [
            { "id": "backpack", "name": "行医背囊", "description": "容量20格（可升级），采药必备", "icon": "🎒" },
            { "id": "copper", "name": "铜钱", "count": 200, "description": "路费与药资", "icon": "💰" },
            { "id": "recommendation", "name": "院长推荐信", "description": "各地药铺、村庄好感度+10", "icon": "📜" },
            { "id": "herb_guide", "name": "本草基础册", "description": "记录已识别草药的图鉴", "icon": "📖" }
          ],
          "nextDelay": 2000
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_006",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "qingmiao",
          "expression": "happy",
          "name": "青苗",
          "text": "（从肩头探头探脑）哇！好多东西！主人以后采的草药都可以放进去吗？！",
          "avatar": "qingmiao_happy.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_007",
          "type": "choice",
          "options": [
            {
              "text": "当然，青苗帮主人找的草药都放这里。",
              "flag": "kind_to_pet",
              "response": {
                "character": "qingmiao",
                "expression": "happy",
                "name": "青苗",
                "text": "（开心得转圈圈）嘿嘿！青苗会努力的！找最好最好的草药给主人！",
                "avatar": "qingmiao_happy.png",
                "nextDelay": 500,
                "nextStep": "S06_008"
              }
