        {
          "id": "S06_008",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "xiaolan",
          "expression": "anxious",
          "name": "小兰",
          "text": "（忽然想起什么，神色紧张）对了！今早翠竹村来了位老婆婆，说村里好多老人都病了，四肢乏力还咳个不停，药铺断货了……",
          "avatar": "xiaolan_anxious.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_009",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "xiaolan",
          "expression": "anxious",
          "name": "小兰",
          "text": "院长脚伤走不得，叫我来问问你……说你正好要出门，能不能顺路去瞧瞧……",
          "avatar": "xiaolan_anxious.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_choice2",
          "type": "choice",
          "options": [
            {
              "text": "翠竹村？我这就去！",
              "flag": "active",
              "response": {
                "character": "xiaolan",
                "expression": "grateful",
                "name": "小兰",
                "text": "（眼眶微红，深深鞠躬）谢谢师兄/师姐！老婆婆一定在等着的……",
                "avatar": "xiaolan_grateful.png",
                "nextDelay": 500,
                "nextStep": "S06_010"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "先说说具体病情，我好做准备。",
              "flag": "cautious",
              "response": {
                "character": "xiaolan",
                "expression": "anxious",
                "name": "小兰",
                "text": "（急得跺脚）说是最初几人咳嗽，后来越来越多人病倒，连村医都没办法了……求你快去吧！",
                "avatar": "xiaolan_anxious.png",
                "nextDelay": 500,
                "nextStep": "S06_010"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_010",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "serious",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "（从门口缓步走来，拄着拐杖）孩子，此行翠竹村，为师只嘱一事——先治病，再传道。百草之行，由此始。",
          "avatar": "bai_serious.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_011",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "bai",
          "expression": "smile",
          "name": "白院长",
          "text": "（目光温和）去吧。为师相信你。记住今日所学，以仁心济世，便是岐黄之道的真谛。",
          "avatar": "bai_smile.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_012",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "xiaolan",
          "expression": "grateful",
          "name": "小兰",
          "text": "（挥手，眼中含泪）师兄/师姐一路平安！……记得平安回来啊！",
          "avatar": "xiaolan_grateful.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "S06_013",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "qingmiao",
          "expression": "happy",
          "name": "青苗",
          "text": "（跳上肩头，兴奋地晃动叶芽）出发啦出发啦！青苗已经感觉到翠竹村方向有好多的……呃，好像也有不好的味道……",
          "avatar": "qingmiao_happy.png",
          "nextDelay": 500,
          "nextScene": "S07"
        }
